#10487 Sooooo… I’m undocumented. With all the shitty stuff that comes from it, I’ve used it as motivation to prove myself capable and aim as close to a 5.0 as possible. Now, with DACA ending and my work permit soon expiring, I feel like my whole world is crumbling. I’ll graduate and have nothing to show for it but a diploma cause I’ll be unemployable. Being the first in my family to even graduate from high school will mean nothing anymore because everything I’ve worked for will lead nowhere. All my motivation is quickly dwindling and I’m starting to see no purpose in even being here anymore :(
